Author: ChiNgadOr
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Dear SKYFchain / SKYF supporters!  With this letter we would like to update you on the project development as well as make you an offer - with the company’s global expansion there is an opportunity to become an official sales representative, the details are below.    SKYFchain update.  After a successful MVP launch in late 2018, the project team is focused on the front-end solution development for the first commercial customers from agricultural industry. There are certain requirements and data-sets specific to this field, and this is what keeps us busy. The first set of SKYFchain SuperNodes was distributed at end of 2018. The development and launch of SuperNode software is postponed for several months due to the current focus.    SKYF Drones Manufacturing.  SKYF has performed multiple demonstration flights in October – December 2018, including the flight with 100 kg load. The next milestone is the flight with 200 kg load, which is planned for February 2019. Let us remind you that this generation of SKYF will have the capacity of 400 kg of useful load. Commercial tests are planned with clients for the agricultural season of 2019.    And here comes your offer.  SKYF is seeking global partners in sales, distribution, operators’ training and service of the drones. We are developing fast in some countries, and with your help we can do even better! Become a certified SKYF representative and get 5% Introduction Fee on any new contract. You do the introduction and once a sales contract is signed and a payment is received, you get the percentage of the deal, whatever the volume is.    What we offer.  Your client exclusivity. No one will approach your target client after you identify the client and we make a deal. Actual sales is done by our team – you initiate the conversation, and can stay involved as long as you consider good for the business. Mind-blowing innovation in unmanned cargo industry, there is no available alternative to SKYF drones. We will provide you with a PDF leaflet with SKYF specs and other materials on demand (Please reach us in telegram channel: https://t.me/SKYFchain_chat ). The commercial sales start in 2020, so the contracting is already underway with some of our partners.  In case you’re interested, please check in at this  form, and we will get in touch.   Sincerely,  SKYFchain / SKYF Team

Author: etherclassic
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Dear Supporters of SKYFchain! The first SuperNode Certificates to the holders of SKYFT tokens were successfully distributed. There is still a chance for those, who missed it - 7 SuperNode are still available at this stage. Become a holder and share the benefits! Below you'll find the key terms and conditions.  SKYFchain SuperNode terms and conditions (valid from Sep 09, 2018 until Dec 31, 2019)  What are the benefits to be a supernode holder in Y1 (until Dec 31, 2019)?  Each supernode certificate will be rewarded with 500 000 SKYFT tokens form the Network Development Fund (NDF) on 31 Dec 2019 for supporting a supernode for the entire year. In case a person holds a supernode certificate only for a part of the year he/she will be rewarded with a proportional part of 500 000 SKYFT tokens (only for the last continuous period). 50% of transaction fee will be distributed amount certificates holders. SKYFchain platform starts transactions in 2019. How to become a supernode holder? Buy up to 1 612 903 SKYFT on BitForex / IDEX or other exchanges where SKYFT is listed. You can also buy tokens from SKYFchain directly if the exchange price exceeds $0,65 per SKYFT. If during pre-ICO you invested 30k into SKYFT tokens (we’ll check your purchasing records) – we need your email confirmation to become a supernode holder to proceed with certificate. If during the main sale of the ICO you invested 100k into SKYFT tokens (we’ll check your purchasing records) – we need your email confirmation to become a supernode holder to proceed with certificate. Present SKYFT tokens balance in your wallet (need to qualify conditions 1,2 or 3) 24h before certificate issue events on 31 Oct 2018, 31 Dec 2018, 31 March 2019, 30 June 2019, or 30 Sept 2019. Present SKYFT tokens balance in your wallet (need to qualify conditions 1,2 or 3) 24h before NDF tokens distribution on 31 Dec 2019. Run your server with no more than 10% downtime (nearly 24/7). One can be a holder of several supernode certificates. What is SKYFchain supernode? SKYFchain supernode is a computer with constant connection to Internet with the following minimum requirements (for Y1): CPU: 2 CORES (intel X38 or similar) RAM: 4GB Storage: 300GB Internet connection: 50 MBS SKYFchain will run SKYFchain software and store date to make it work stable and secure. Supernode technical requirements are the subject of change due to constant development of SKYFchain and growth of transaction volume.  If you are interested and agreed with terms and conditions, please reply to info@skyfchain.io

Author: viettelpay
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: We are happy to disclose that Russia-based SKYF drone manufacturing company and Turkey-based TANDEM DEFENSE LTD agreed to become partners to enter the Turkish market of unmanned vehicles. TANDEM LTD becomes SKYF’s commercial representative for the marketing, promotion and sales of the drones in Turkey. The company will also prospect and solicit orders from existing and new customers and negotiate the deals on behalf of the company. “Turkish market promises great opportunities for SKYF. We’re very excited about this agreement and hope that TANDEM DEFENSE LTD will be able to make our product highly demanded in this region”  , said Alexander Timofeev, SKYFChain CEO. “SKYF heavy lifting drones are known for outstanding characteristics. We are proud and excited with the opportunity to become the commercial representative of SKYF in Turkey” said Hüseyin Cahit DEMİR,  TANDEM DEFENSE LTD’s Founding Partner. TANDEM DEFENSE LTD was founded in 2018 and the company partners have 19 years of experience in the Aviation markets. The company was established as a sister company to SVK Industries Ltd which focuses on Air Traffic Control systems and Electronics.

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: ♨️ CargoCoin and SKYFchain Join Forces!   CargoCoin and SKYFchain has signed the MOU (Memorandum of Understanding) and reached an agreement to work on the integration of both blockchain-powered platforms for unmanned logistics.   The platforms are highly complementary to each other – while SKYFchain provides a platform for industrial logistics operations of unmanned cargo vehicles – drones, trucks and ships, CargoCoin offers a paperless solution for the document flow in cargo transportation. SKYFchain deals with unmanned vehicles and CargoCoin takes care of the load, which together is a total autonomous logistics solution. Users of both platforms will get access to the services and providers on both, doubling the speed of adoption of the unmanned approach.   CEO of CargoCoin Bogomil Alexandrov said: "SKYFChain is a pioneer company in the field of unmanned drone flights and we find their products to be of outstanding quality and technology, which will be a future of transport. We have great expectations for the benefits of this cooperation for both CargoCoin & SKYFchain, together we will shape the future of blockchain based cargo and logistics."   CEO of SKYFchain Alexander Timofeev said: “We are happy to find a reliable partner in the emerging field of blockchain-based logistics. CargoCoin is an industry pioneer and can provide our clients with an easy global service. Together we are offering an end-to-end solution to our customers.”  www.skyfchain.io  https://s6.wampi.ru/2018/07/17/9-01.md.jpg

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: ♨️ SKYFchain Releases Alfa Version Of The Business-2-Robots Logistics Platform  Alfa version of SKYFchain, the first Business-2-Robots operating platform, is now available at mvp.skyfchain.io. The software is the result of joint efforts of SKYFchain and QIWI Blockchain Technology.  Over the last months, SKYFchain team held hundreds of meetings and negotiations with potential partners and clients building the business network and creating demand for SKYFT tokens among the leading companies, institutions and state entities around the globe. The accumulated knowledge of the market expectations towards our product and business plan helped us create the technical specifications for the Yellow Paper and Minimal Viable Product.  The alfa version of the platform includes some core features. It provides the user with a selection of eight system account profiles, ranging from a drone manufacturer and service company to a bank or an underwriter. After signing in, users are steered to the dashboard where one can check and manage the autonomous vehicles (drones for now) on missions.  The system sorts available vehicles by transport type, make, model, carrying capacities, geo locations and time remaining to planned maintenance. Drones on missions are sorted by type, mission, route and some additional parameters.  Users can check the profile of every vehicle in the system. The data includes cost, technical parameters, documents and certifications for the machine, geo locations’ and routes log, history and details of transactions, missions completed and technical maintenances records. User’s account shows the balance sheet and deposited funds in multiple currencies.  The MVP is available by link: mvp.skyfchain.io. To enter the system, choose the Logistics Operator role. The credentials are filled in automatically.  'We believe that the core value of our product is concluded not in a program code but the understanding the business processes of unmanned logistics and building up interaction with customers. Now, we launch the prototype and intensively continue work in this direction', - Alexander Timofeev, SKYFchain's CEO says.  www.skyfchain.io  https://s6.wampi.ru/2018/06/25/3-01.md.jpg

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: We know about several competitors of ours. We actually want to try to partner with them at some point. Here they are:  AirMap - The platform that powers drone flights - focuses on visualizing areas on the map for drones navigation SKYFchain will additionaly have logistics smart-contracts, insurance and financing features  Flock – Pay-as-you-fly drone insurance - chooses the safest flight path and allows drone insurance SKYFchain will additionaly have logistics smart-contracts, drone lyfecycle management and financing features  Botlink - drone mapping software that captures data, analyzes it, and reacts quickly - allows to create detailed surface maps SKYFchain will instead have itinenary verification, logistics smart-contracts, drone lyfecycle management, insurance and financing features

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: ♨️ We have great news!  💢 Small-scale production of SKYF cargo drones are launching  ARDN Technology, a Russian company, has tripled its production site to start the release of a prototype series of SKYF drones! The first drones will be used to run tests, including shipping to the first clients. The first mass production of cargo.  "We have expanded our experimental production site in Kazan and now we are able to produce 3-4 drones per month. The first party of the drones will be used for testing in various areas, from field processing and cargo delivery to water-bombing fire extinguishing. On the first party, we will work out all the conditions and tasks possible. This will allow us to accelerate the creation of the final design of the drone, the utter version. With it, the first mass production of unmanned aerial cargo platforms in Russia will be launched in 2020, "explained Alexander Timofeev, ARDN Technology and SKYFchain CEO.  We want remind: SKYF is an unmanned aerial platform for vertical take-off and landing. At the moment, the drone's payload capacity is up to 400 kg, its flight range is up to 350 km, and the flight duration is up to 8 hours (with a payload of 50 kg).  https://www.skyfchain.io  https://s5.wampi.ru/2018/05/28/311bf0fc6a0b6400b.md.jpg

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: We know about several competitors of ours. We actually want to try to partner with them at some point. Here they are:  AirMap - The platform that powers drone flights - focuses on visualizing areas on the map for drones navigation SKYFchain will additionaly have logistics smart-contracts, insurance and financing features  Flock – Pay-as-you-fly drone insurance - chooses the safest flight path and allows drone insurance SKYFchain will additionaly have logistics smart-contracts, drone lyfecycle management and financing features  Botlink - drone mapping software that captures data, analyzes it, and reacts quickly - allows to create detailed surface maps SKYFchain will instead have itinenary verification, logistics smart-contracts, drone lyfecycle management, insurance and financing features

We are happy to inform you of the improvements we’ve made to the interface and functionality of Investor’s Account Dashboard, live as of 02.05.2018. Following the community’s feedback, the new dashboard has become more secure and user-friendly. The main changes are the fresh and simpler interface and added optional 2-factor authentication for enhanced security.  There is also a new algorithm for referral bonuses – not only early investors receive 5% commission from all the attracted investments of their friends and followers, who registered with the referral code, but they also continue to receive bonuses from the second level of followers of their followers (2%) and even the third level of investors (1%). We do hope this will increase the stakes of all early investors and give better incentives for bringing in your friends and colleagues. Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Translated in English  In the framework of the 11th International helicopter industry exhibition HeliRussia 2018 , where in addition to helicopters every year new unmanned aerial vehicles are demonstrated, the world's first commercial multi-rotor SKYF air cargo platform will be presented for the first time .   Designed by Kazan Design Bureau "Avioreheniya" , SKYF is intended specifically for the transport of goods. The maximum carrying capacity of the passing test of the device is up to 250 kg, while with a cargo of 50 kg the flight range reaches 350 km, and the flight duration - up to 8 hours .   In addition to cargo transportation, the capabilities of the SKYF air cargo platform make it possible to apply itfor processing agricultural fields and for air extinguishing . Efficiency and safety of aviation operations are provided by a unique patented aerodynamic scheme with separation of lifting and operating screws , a new control model, modern equipment and software. The advantages of using SKYF in the interests of farmers will be presented at the 1st All-Russian Conference on the Development of Agricultural Aviation, which will be held on May 24 as part of HeliRussia 2018.   The development of the SKYF platform began in 2014, and the first flight of the full-size prototype took place in the spring of 2016. Now more than 30 experts take part in the development of the platform, testing and improving the model, which differs significantly from other multi-rotor systems, is equipped with a gasoline engine and has full autonomy. HeliRussia 2018 will feature a fully operational prototype SKYF, participating in flight tests.   Visitors of the exhibition and journalists are invited to take part in the presentation of the SKYF unmanned vehicle, which will be held on May 24 at 10:30 on the stand of OKB Aviaresheniya (5L).

Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: 📝 SKYF Heavy Lifting Drones to Transport Goods in Vietnamese Seaport  Russia-based SKYF drone manufacturing company and Vietnam-based International Transportation and Trading Company (ITC) agreed to become partners. ITC plans to launch a service for unmanned aerial cargo logistics with SKYF heavy lifting drones and invest the purchasing of two SKYF drones for testing. The deal will be completed by the end of 2019. Now the partners are sketching a road map and preparing the paperwork according to the national regulation rules.  At the moment, the primary service of ITC is the waterway transportation. Currently, ITC owns and operates 02 160 TEUs Barge with total capacity of 320 TEUs per turn. Besides, ITC operates inland transport division which has 140 tractors and 160 trailers.  ITC considers new opportunities opening with the growing of the unmanned cargo logistics market. Thus, the company will purchase SKYF heavy lifting drones. The aim of ITC is to expand the set of goods transportation services being provided and to gain a competitive advantages on the regional logistics market.  📄 Read more: https://www.newsbtc.com/2018/04/20/skyf-heavy-lifting-drones-transport-goods-vietnamese-seaport/  https://s2.wampi.ru/2018/04/20/photo_2018-04-20_14-16-30.md.jpg

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: 📝 SKYFchain: Communication with Drones Made Reliable  The logistics industry in 2018 is a field hungry for innovations. Its main problem is still the human labor: not only is it pricey, but it is also not productive. That’s why Amazon has started using drones in their storehouses as they are more efficient and way cheaper in the long run.  In Russia, SKYF company is in the avant-garde of implementing unmanned carrier platforms. They have run several successful tests in the farming sector already, and with each passing day, SKYF gets more clients. But the problem is: if we use the unmanned carrier platforms, who will be in control of the operations done by the drones? How to make the system transparent for all counterparts? SKYF has figured out: blockchain is the ultimate solution.  📄 Read more: https://www.newsbtc.com/2018/03/28/skyfchain-communication-drones-made-reliable/#  https://s1.wampi.ru/2018/03/29/2903-2.md.jpg

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: In July 2017 the president's spokesperson Dmitry Peskov said that it was time for the government to start regulating the legal issues of robotics and artificial intelligence.  However, it is not clear how the government will be able to solve this problem!  The co-founder of Mail.Ru and Grishin Robotics Dmitry Grishin, for example, has proposed to create a register of robots and punish their owners or manufacturers, depending on the harm done…  While implementing the project SKYFchain we strive to minimize unexpected situations that may arise in the use of robotics for freight or other transportation.  Thanks to the use of blockchain, any member of the system will always be able to get detailed information about a particular robot-to find out whether it has licenses, whether it has passed maintenance, and so on…  We would also like to remind you that all the information about our project can be found in the following links:  Official website: https://SKYFchain.io/  Link to the up-to-date White Paper: https://fpivc.app.box.com/v/SKYFchainWhitePaper  Telegram chat of the project: https://t.me/SKYFchain_chat  Github: https://github.com/SKYFchain/skyfchain?files=1  https://c.radikal.ru/c42/1803/c7/9793247aa958.jpg

Thank you for supporting our project!  Here is a quick recap:  👉 Our ICO was launched 1 March 2018.  👉 500,000 USD was raised before the official sales launch;  👉 By the morning of 4 March 2018 we reached 1,000,000 USD;  👉 2,000,000 USD was raised on March 6;  👉 As of now SKYFchain pre-ICO was supported by over 4000 people.  “I am happy to see that our vision about deployment of unmanned logistic on the blockchain is well accepted by community”, SKYFchain’s CEO Alexander Timofeev says. Author: juvsotto
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Why drones need maintenance?  Aircrafts, and drones as well, are expensive specialized equipment. The price of a single such vehicle (even a used one) can reach as high as several hundred thousand, or even millions of US dollars. That’s why, buying such an object, a customer must be completely sure that he possesses valid data on the equipment and that all the terms of the deal will be adhered to 100%. Oftentimes a customer and an object of purchase are situated in different regions, so it isn’t easy to come to the place and inspect the object. It becomes even more difficult if these are different countries or continents…  SKYFchain project develops a unique decentralized platform, which will allow its users to get full and valid data on equipment. Despite this seeming quite pompous, in fact it will be very easy. Distributed register based on blockchain, incorporated in the platform, will store all the data on technical conditions of drones and history of their usage – from certification to technical checkups and passports.

Body: The common problem for most of the developers is accessing medical data for training of their neural networks. Skychain will provide a special function of hosting of medical datasets in a closed-loop system, and the ability to teach third-party neural networks, using these datasets. The datasets will be kept in safety and remain the property of their owners, as well as the neural networks. It also guarantees the receipt of a fee for each use of the neural network both for developers and for the providers of datasets, which were used for training of neural networks. Large corporations, such as IBM, are not able to independently train thousands of neural networks needed to fully cover all areas of medical diagnostics. Skychain will contain thousands or even tens of thousands of highly specialized neural networks created by independent laboratories and corporations.

Author: charmperez28
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Skychain is a "distributed open network" project designed to accurately diagnose patients and prescribe effective treatment. Skychain has the following advantages:  Uploading any ANNs trained by laboratories or specialists to Skychain and receiving payment from end users of ANNs  It's a data marketplace as Service for Deep Learning, where medical data suppliers will be able to offer their datasets as a service for AANs training;  Effective use of miners’ computing resources to ensure smooth operation of a neural network;  Public pay-per-use access to the neural network capabilities;  Open distributed storage of all ANNs within Skychain and their settings, stored in a distributed chain of blocks according to the blockchain principles;  Constant learning of a neural network upon adding new information and experience.

Author: charmperez28
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Skychain stores all information about all ANNs within Skychain in an encrypted form. Any specialist or company will be able to upload their neural network to Skychain, designed and trained to effectively solve a particular task. Then, an author of the uploaded neural network will be remunerated by Skychain participants at each access to the services of his ANN. Data marketplace Skychain for medical data providers is a data marketplace where they can provide their data as a service for training of third-party neural networks:  Trained neural networks on the supplier data sets can only be used within Skychain, so the date set providers will receive a guaranteed share of revenue from all neural networks trained based on their data;  Preparation of medical data sets will be beneficial for market participants who own such data. Skychain takes care of the intellectual property of developers of neural networks and data owners. The developed and trained neural network, as well as the data set with which it was trained, are protected from outside participants

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: There are no pilots flying a SKYF. All flight missions are preloaded in a flight plan before the drone takes off. Blockchain technology and multiple verification protocols are used to ensure proper use of the drone. To prevent unauthorized use of SKYF, a multilevel protection system was implemented. That system requires several independent elements to operate: an operator's key, a flight mission signed in the control center, hardware protection against a controller and autopilot replacement, and protection of SKYF datalink from interception.   We are also building a blockchain ecosystem SKYFchain that verifies the authenticity of parts and construction of the drones prior to providing the right of operation for each flight.

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: We have already talked about how drones are often perceived as having use strictly in the military field as unmanned vehicles, which in reality is being slowly displaced as their primary use as drones enter our daily lives. These flying devices are being used in advertisement, filming, delivery, and as time goes by they become more and more accessible, paving way for more unusual ideas!  Recently the world has started to see drones used in livestock farming. The idea here is that such a drone can follow its designated target while evading obstacles they meet in the air. Such flying robots can reach speeds of 70 km/h with a battery life of around 30 minutes. Since livestock farmers found out about this technology, the task of finding and taking a stray animal back home has become way easier. NOAA researchers even use drones to keep track of dolphins in Hawaiian waters.  Our drone — the SKYF Unmanned Aerial Carrier is more universal. You can see regular posting on our social media — pictures demonstrating UAC features and capabilities. It’s the first vertical take-off and landing load-carrying industrial-grade drone on the market. The words load-carrying are backed up with its impressive ability to carry up to 400kg, as well as fly long distances as far as 350km!  https://www.skyfchain.io/

Body: Our subscribers, of course, remember that we have participated in CES and were very pleased with how it went. However, ROBOGEEK decided to cover the conference in more detail and talk about all the Russian drones showcased in Vegas! We have decided to refresh both your and our memories regarding CES, where we went to showcase our technological achievements to the audience of the world’s largest hi-tech show. We wanted to get feedback from both the tech and investment community, assess the level of interest around this market, and draw the attention of international journalists.  We have completed these tasks and even got in direct contact with Nevada Test Center to discuss the possibility of running some test flights of our SKYF drone.  See more information in the article titled “Russian drones in Vegas” http://www.robogeek.ru/letayuschie-roboty/russkie-drony-v-vegase#  https://www.skyfchain.io/

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Did you know that researchers from the University of Zurich have developed an algorithm that will turn drones into full participants of the urban traffic?  They have developed DroNet – a unique neural network software which controls the drone, and is is trained to recognize dangerous situations and respond quickly. It is interesting that instead of a set of some science-fiction sensors to monitor its surroundings, the system relies on a conventional camera.  In addition to that, after training in the urban environment it turnout out that unmanned aerial vehicles can utilize this knowledge in other complicated situations: in parking lots and office corridors.  There is only one “but” – the adoption of this technology is far away still…  https://www.skyfchain.io/

Body: It’s time to tell you about aerial vehicle SKYF UAC in more detail – its mass production and distribution will help to develop and test SKYFchain Fintech Platform.   SKYF Unmanned Aerial Carrier (UAC) is the first industrial cargo drone with vertical take-off and landing. It works on a classic petrol engine, and as of now is unmatched in its capabilities by any known unmanned solutions. It can carry an ultrahigh load (up to 250 kg) and conduct extended flights (up to 350 km).  SKYF UAC can be used in several market segments, including logistics, agriculture and firefighting… We expect that by 2021 over a thousand UAC SKYFs will operate across the world. But we’d like to remind you that SKYF UAC will be just one of many participants of the platform we’re developing and it will be open for all the participants of cargo drones industry.  These are operators and clients, aerial vehicle manufacturers, licensees and technical services, controlling bodies and market analysts. Subscribe to our social media, soon we’re going to post a video of SKYF UAC flights – you can’t miss this!  http://skyfchain.io/

Author: SKYFchain
Title: [ANN][ICO]SKYFchain is the first B2R blockchain based operating platform
Body: Why drones need maintenance?  Aircrafts, and drones as well, are expensive specialized equipment. The price of a single such vehicle (even a used one) can reach as high as several hundred thousand, or even millions of US dollars. That’s why, buying such an object, a customer must be completely sure that he possesses valid data on the equipment and that all the terms of the deal will be adhered to 100%. Oftentimes a customer and an object of purchase are situated in different regions, so it isn’t easy to come to the place and inspect the object. It becomes even more difficult if these are different countries or continents…  SKYFchain project develops a unique decentralized platform, which will allow its users to get full and valid data on equipment. Despite this seeming quite pompous, in fact it will be very easy. Distributed register based on blockchain, incorporated in the platform, will store all the data on technical conditions of drones and history of their usage – from certification to technical checkups and passports.  Every user of the platform – individual and corporate clients, insurance companies, drone operators, state agencies, cargo transportation customers and cargo owners, will be able to get an access to this vast array of information at any moment and find needed data on an interested object, being totally sure in the accuracy of provided data.

Body: Drones have gained popularity over the past few years — this is no surprise as they are capable of performing many functions. Today we’re presenting top 10 of the most expensive drones in the world.  · EHang 184 Price tag: $300 000 Chinese design — Unmanned Aerial Vehicle capable of carrying one passenger Will hit the market in the next 3–5 years  · Xact Sense Titan Price tag: $120 000 Octocopter designed for area surveying and mapping  · XactSense MAX 8 Price tag: $65 000 Another octocopter with a great usage potential: in agriculture, for video- and photoshooting, as well as mapping  · AEE F100 Price tag: $58 000 Quadcopter for film- and photoshooting, security measures and land surveying  · AEE F50 Price tag: $37 000 Quadcopter of an earlier generation with functions similar to AEE F100, but the cost is 1.5 times less  · CyberQuad MAXI Price tag: $37 000 Quadcopter with protected propellers. For a wide range of users: from military and emergency services to environment protectionists and cameramen  · G4 Eagle V2 Cargo Price tag: $35 360 Octocopter designed to deliver cargo and mail packages  · Draganfly Draganflyer X4-ES Price tag: $25 000 Quadcopter for mapping, photo- and videoshooting and ensuring security  · Advanced Tactics Inc Transformer UGAV Price tag: $25 000 Hexacopter-transformer equipped with stable wheels for ground riding. Among offered usages — videoshooting and ensuring security.  · Lockheed Martin Indago Price tag: $25 000 Drone helping to ensure public safety  As you’ve noticed, many of these drones are yet to appear on the market, while our vehicle — SKYF Unmanned Aerial Carrier (UAC) is already flying and surpasses many of them in capabilities! Our drone is able of a vertical take-off and landing, transports cargo of up to 250 kg and flies at a distance of up to 350 km… There can be a plenty of “expensive” drones, but SKYF is the best by many features!  https://www.skyfchain.io/
